						Response to Questions (40%)</p>
				</td>
				<td style="background: rgb(217, 217, 217); border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext currentColor; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 5.4pt; width: 111px;">
					<p>
						Quizzes</p>
				</td>
			</tr>
